Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 16:21:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/6] Add a wl_output global per screen

Advertise a version 4 wl_output for every NSScreen, sending geometry,
mode, scale, name and description as appropriate for the version the
client binds. Clients like foot refuse to start without a wl_output.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_0187CcHcrnoWzf7rzCaEDpR1
